
Installation instructions / Installationshinweise
-------------------------------------------------

Complete installation instructions are contained in the user manual
in documentation/en/download2.html.

Vollständige Installationshinweise befinden sich im Benutzerhandbuch
in documentation/de/download2.html.


For the very impatient:
-----------------------

Unpack the archive, cd into the directory, type './configure; make':

tar xzf dvdisaster-0.50.0.tgz
cd dvdisaster-0.50.0
./configure
make
./dvdisaster

Working with the program from the current directory is okay.


Optionally, install the program 
(do ./configure --help for changing the installation locations)

make install


Enjoy using dvdisaster!
